description:
Colors_LIVE is the first live DVD from Between the Buried and Me that will be released on October 14, 2008. The concert was filmed at the Rocketown in Nashville, Tennessee on Friday, August 2, 2008.

The band played two sets during the concert - the first included the band&amp;#039;s most recent Colors album in its entirety and the second was of previously released songs. The DVD will include both sets. An audio CD will come with the DVD including the Colors live set.

Track listing

1. &quot;Foam Born (a): The Backtrack&quot;
2. &quot;Foam Born (b): The Decade of Statues&quot;
3. &quot;Informal Gluttony&quot;
4. &quot;Sun of Nothing&quot;
5. &quot;Ants of the Sky&quot;
6. &quot;Prequel to the Sequel&quot;
7. &quot;Viridian&quot;
8. &quot;White Walls&quot;
